species-name-resomi = Resomi
species-description-resomi = Resomi are a species of humanoid, feline-like creatures with a wide variety of fur colors and patterns. They are known for their agility and keen senses, making them excellent hunters and climbers. Resomi have a strong connection to nature and are often found in forested areas, where they live in harmony with the environment. They are social creatures, often forming close-knit communities and valuing family bonds. Resomi are also known for their playful and curious nature, often exploring their surroundings with great enthusiasm.
